## Version 1.6 Implementation

### Goal

Add a delete and clear all button to webview of SourceDoc. 

### Delete Button
This should show up for each codeblock within the webview
- Trash Icon in the top right of each code block
- Deletes SourceDoc Codeblock from save JSON, and file. 

### Clear All Button
This should show up at the top of the webview which allows of clearing all of the codeblocks associated with the viewed file
- ClearAll button at the top of the webview
- Confirmation to delete all codeblock documentation/markers
